title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 3 2022
description:
Free speech has rarely been more at risk. Joy Reid smears Rush, but admits he was the greatest. Elon Musk goes to Met Gala, shares his vision for Twitter. Former Trump economic adviser Stephen Moore joins Buck to talk about the economy, how we could avoid a recession, Biden's clueless economic team. Buck takes a call on the abortion debate to close out the program.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
